cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG

The paper focuses on text-entry on mobile devices, which is a human-computer interaction (HCI) topic, making cs.HC the most likely category. The use of a deep neural decoder (DND) also suggests a connection to natural language processing (NLP), which falls under cs.CL. The paper also mentions collecting user data and conducting simulations and experiments, which could involve computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
